     C* Phase 3 cycle test: sum AMT across records, return at LR.
     C* Data file DATA has records '010','020','005','007' -> sum 42.
     FDATA    IP  F    80              DISK
     IDATA    AA  01
     I                                        1   30AMT
     C                     ADD  AMT       RPGRET
     C* (LR total time: RPGRET holds the accumulated sum)
     CLR                   SETOF
